ings. Produce action items and follow up. Help ensure that all entities of the organization are coordinated and properly functioning Maintain the Raleigh office and day-to-day operations which are on par with brand protocol. Preferred Skills A Bachelor's degree or current enrollment in a college or university. 0-4 years of experience in an operations management or communications role. Experience or understanding of Google Docs and communications tools such as Zoom. Strong communications skills, both verbal and written. Pick up new skills quickly. Confidence in the ability to keep items and tasks properly organized. Job Types: Full-time, Internship Schedule: Monday to Friday Work Location: One location Internship Compensation: Pay Company's website: https://www.blockchaincenter.com/ Company's Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/Blockcentercom Work Remotely: No ", 
